         Jain Irrigation Systems Limited (JISL or the Company) is one of Indias largest integrated agribusiness players, with operations in Micro Irrigation Systems (MIS), plastic pipes and sheets, dehydrated vegetables, processed fruits and other smaller businesses including tissue culture, agri-tech solutions and green energy. It is headquartered in Jalgaon in the western Indian state of Maharashtra. JISL is Indias leader in Micro Irrigation Systems and the second largest globally; it is also the largest manufacturer of plastic pipes in India. 


         The Company had revenues of approximately US$ 1 billion for the last financial year (FY) ended March 31, 2017 and had a market capitalization of approximately US$ 930 million as of February 2, 2018.

