         JISL and its subsidiaries operate production facilities for MIS, plastic pipes, plastic sheets, tissue culture dehydrated vegetables and processed fruits in Maharashtra, Andhra Pradesh, Tamil Nadu, Gujarat and Rajasthan of India and has also invested in other subsidiaries overseas including the United States, UK, Turkey, and Israel.  The proposed IFC financing will support JISLs operations in India.
